trans-unit.source: Provides information on processes currently executing.
trans-unit.target: 提供目前正在執行的處理序相關資訊。

trans-unit.source: This class returns information about ASP.NET worker processes that are running under the ASP.NET process model.
trans-unit.target: 這個類別會傳回 ASP.NET 處理序模型下執行 ASP.NET 工作者處理序的相關資訊。

trans-unit.source: Objects of this type are returned by the static methods <xref:System.Web.ProcessModelInfo.GetCurrentProcessInfo%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> and <xref:System.Web.ProcessModelInfo.GetHistory%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>.
trans-unit.target: 此類型的物件所傳回的靜態方法<xref:System.Web.ProcessModelInfo.GetCurrentProcessInfo%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>和<xref:System.Web.ProcessModelInfo.GetHistory%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>。

trans-unit.source: These methods are the only useful ways to create an initialized object.
trans-unit.target: 這些方法是建立初始化的物件的唯一有用的方式。

trans-unit.source: If you are using Microsoft Internet Information Services (IIS) 6.0, process metrics returned by the <xref:System.Web.ProcessInfo> classes are available only if you are running in IIS 5.0 isolation mode.
trans-unit.target: 如果您使用 Microsoft 網際網路資訊服務 (IIS) 6.0，處理所傳回的度量<xref:System.Web.ProcessInfo>類別是您在 IIS 5.0 隔離模式執行時，才可以使用。

trans-unit.source: If you are using IIS 6.0 in worker process isolation mode, the ASP.NET process model is disabled and an <xref:System.Web.HttpException> exception is thrown when you access <xref:System.Web.ProcessInfo> members.
trans-unit.target: 如果您使用 IIS 6.0 工作者處理序隔離模式中，會停用 ASP.NET 處理序模型和<xref:System.Web.HttpException>存取時，會擲回例外狀況<xref:System.Web.ProcessInfo>成員。

trans-unit.source: The following code example demonstrates using the <xref:System.Web.ProcessInfo.Age%2A>, <xref:System.Web.ProcessInfo.PeakMemoryUsed%2A>, <xref:System.Web.ProcessInfo.ProcessID%2A>, <xref:System.Web.ProcessInfo.RequestCount%2A>, <xref:System.Web.ProcessInfo.ShutdownReason%2A>, <xref:System.Web.ProcessInfo.StartTime%2A> and <xref:System.Web.ProcessInfo.Status%2A> properties of the <xref:System.Web.ProcessInfo> class.
trans-unit.target: 下列程式碼範例示範如何使用<xref:System.Web.ProcessInfo.Age%2A>， <xref:System.Web.ProcessInfo.PeakMemoryUsed%2A>， <xref:System.Web.ProcessInfo.ProcessID%2A>， <xref:System.Web.ProcessInfo.RequestCount%2A>， <xref:System.Web.ProcessInfo.ShutdownReason%2A>，<xref:System.Web.ProcessInfo.StartTime%2A>和<xref:System.Web.ProcessInfo.Status%2A>屬性<xref:System.Web.ProcessInfo>類別。

trans-unit.source: The example displays a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinkButton>.
trans-unit.target: 此範例會顯示<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinkButton>。

trans-unit.source: When the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinkButton> is clicked, the current process information is displayed.
trans-unit.target: 當<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinkButton>按一下時，目前處理程序資訊會顯示。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.ProcessInfo" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.Web.ProcessInfo" /> 類別的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.ProcessInfo" /> class.

trans-unit.source: Objects of this type are returned by the `static` methods <xref:System.Web.ProcessModelInfo.GetCurrentProcessInfo%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> and <xref:System.Web.ProcessModelInfo.GetHistory%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.DateTime" /> that indicates the time at which the process started.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.DateTime" />，表示處理序開始的時間。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.TimeSpan" /> that indicates the time elapsed since the process started.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.TimeSpan" />，表示自從處理序開始後所經過的時間。

trans-unit.source: The ID number assigned to the process.
trans-unit.target: ID 編號，指派給處理序。

trans-unit.source: The number of start requests for the process.
trans-unit.target: 處理序的開始要求數。

trans-unit.source: One of the <see cref="T:System.Web.ProcessStatus" /> values that indicates the current status of the process.
trans-unit.target: 其中一個 <see cref="T:System.Web.ProcessStatus" /> 值，表示處理序的目前狀態。

trans-unit.source: One of the <see cref="T:System.Web.ProcessShutdownReason" /> values.
trans-unit.target: 其中一個 <see cref="T:System.Web.ProcessShutdownReason" /> 值。

trans-unit.source: The maximum memory used, in kilobytes (KB).
trans-unit.target: 所使用的最大記憶體容量 (以 KB 為單位)。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.ProcessInfo" /> class and sets internal information indicating the status of the process.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.Web.ProcessInfo" /> 類別的新執行個體，並設定指示處理序狀態的內部資訊。
